entry.title: El Salvador's President Went All In on Bitcoin. Then It Tanked.
entry.content: Bitcoin’s losses stoke growing fears of a debt default under President Nayib Bukele.

entry.title: Ukraine Launches Counteroffensive to Disrupt Russian Supply Lines
entry.content: Ukrainian forces continued clearing villages north of Kharkiv, as President Vladimir Putin warned Finland’s leader that joining NATO would risk damaging ties with Moscow, and GOP senators visited Kyiv.

entry.title: Rising Food Prices Roil Developing World
entry.content: Soaring prices are triggering shortages and protests as disruption from the Ukraine war adds to existing strains on global supplies of grains, meat and other foodstuffs.
